{"tid":1008510,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"五兄弟漢堡 five guys 食評","createTime":"2019-02-04T14:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T17:50:30.000Z","uid":21545,"like":28,"dislike":162,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"15fbaf6b3961c7e3999617be5c2f620893305c9f","tid":1008510,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T14:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D5bXWFr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD5bXWFr.png&h=744125b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日放咗學 決定去食餐好送狗年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是去咗排five guys<br />\n我叫咗一個 bacon cheeseburger $98加一杯可樂 $30同一個regular size fries $30<br />\n埋單$158 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貴到 ...<br />\n<br />\n味道方面 ：漢堡包好一般同shake shack 差唔多 塊扒都有啲肉汁 包有烘過 蔬菜冇爛 基本嘢都做足咁 不過咁嘅價錢有係正常 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n汽水簡直同搶冇分別 雖然任飲 但$30/杯 有冇貴咗啲啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n薯條用荷蘭薯 幾大分 即炸 幾好食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n花生任食 味道幾香<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n評分：4/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總結：味道一般 唔洗特登去排隊食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847dc05854b4da0d2c2372f09e2bbc2d1e07f87e","tid":1008510,"uid":192730,"like":167,"dislike":3,"score":164,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T14:11:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">臨近歲晚 走去打劫<br />\n橫批 南亞仔</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4869431d0f07799b12ce06ccbc18687488628188","tid":1008510,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T14:13:44.000Z","msg":"排長龍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/